&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be user obsessed &lt;/strong&gt;- Empathetic, inquisitive, practical&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;About the role:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Goodnotes, we&#39;re on a mission to create the best medium for human and AI collaboration. You will join a talented, distributed Growth Marketing team across Europe and Asia, looking after ASO, Performance Marketing, and CRM. You will work alongside other marketers, designers, and the wider Goodnotes team to acquire new users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As our User Acquisition Manager, you will own the execution of our paid acquisition program across global markets — managing campaigns, measurement infrastructure, and experimentation. This role sits within a structured capital allocation framework - you’re expected to understand and contribute to market-level unit economics (payback windows, LTV/CAC, ROAS by market) that determines where we invest, not just how individual campaigns perform. You’ll work closely with Data Science, Product, and the broader Marketing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This role will initially be offered as a 1 year fixed-term contract&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is a hybrid role with 3 days per week onsite in our Singapore office&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is the role for you, if you’re excited to work on the things listed below:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan, launch, and optimize paid campaigns across Google Ads, Apple Ads, Meta Ads, and other platforms — driving efficient user growth across global markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own market-level unit economics reporting — tracking 1Y ROAS, payback period, and LTV/CAC — and translate insights into concrete optimization decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage our MMP setup (Appsflyer or equivalent) and partner with Data Science on attribution models, including SKAdNetwork and multi-touch attribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and run incrementality measurement via geo holdout tests with Data Science&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage budgets within defined guardrails, reallocating capital across markets based on performance thresholds and pausing investment where markets fall below hurdle rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive a structured experimentation pipeline across ad platforms, from hypothesis through to verdict and next action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The skills you will need to be successful in the above:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on experience in user acquisition, with proven success scaling paid programs across global markets&lt;/li&gt;
